@startuml
!include ../plantuml-theme.iuml
left to right direction

title 图 2.1 用户与组织管理用例图

actor "普通用户" as User
actor "管理员" as Admin
Admin -|> User

rectangle "用户与组织管理模块" {
  usecase "用户注册" as UC_Register
  usecase "用户登录" as UC_Login
  usecase "用户登出" as UC_Logout
  usecase "当前用户信息查询" as UC_Profile
  usecase "切换主组织" as UC_SwitchOrg
  usecase "私人组织标签初始化" as UC_InitPrivate
  usecase "组织标签管理" as UC_OrgManage
  usecase "用户管理" as UC_UserManage
  usecase "用户访问范围配置" as UC_Scope
}

User --> UC_Register
User --> UC_Login
User --> UC_Logout
User --> UC_Profile
User --> UC_SwitchOrg

Admin --> UC_OrgManage
Admin --> UC_UserManage
Admin --> UC_Scope

UC_Register .> UC_InitPrivate : <<include>>

legend bottom
第 2 章只保留需求视角，
不引入 RAG 对话、大模型 API 或后端服务参与者。
endlegend
@enduml
